ack.title: ACKNOWLEDGMENTS
ack.p: We thank the staff at the Environmental Health Hazards Directorate, of the Department of Health, Western Australia, past and present, for the collection, identification, and processing of mosquito samples for virus isolation over the course of the Western Australian arbovirus surveillance program. We acknowledge the assistance of the Surveillance Unit of PathWest, Western Australia, in particular, Avram Levy, for providing access to the MiSeq machine that provided sequence data for this study. We also thank Cheryl Johansen, formerly of the PathWest Surveillance unit of Western Australia, for direct assistance with acquiring virus isolates and for helpful insights.
